  ${
    $d J m n u $.  $d X m n u $.  $d Y m n u $.
    tlmconst.1 $e |- X = U. J $.
    $( A constant sequence converges to the constant.  (Contributed by Jeff
       Madsen, 2-Sep-2009.) $)
    tlmconst $p |- ( ( J e. Top /\ Y e. X ) ->
                                    ( NN X. { Y } ) ( ~~>t ` J ) Y ) $=
      ( vm vu vn wcel wa cn cfv wf cv cuz wral wss c1 wceq adantll adantlr ctop
      csn cxp ctlm wbr wrex cnei w3a fconstg snssi fss syl2anc adantl simpr 1nn
      elnnuz fvconst2g ssnei snssg biimpar syldan adantr eqeltrd sylan2br fveq2
      ralrimiva raleqdv rcla4ev sylancr 3jca tlmbr mpbird ) AUAHZCBHZIZJCUBZUCZ
      CAUDKUEJBVQLZVNEMZVQKZFMZHZEGMZNKZOZGJUFZFVPAUGKKZOZUHVOVRVNWHVNVRVMVNJVP
