      EWKVSWKHWJVSJHZWBVSUPWJWMIVTCWAVOWMVTCRZWIVNWMWNVMJCVSBUQSTWJCWAHZWMVOWIV
      PWAPZWOVMWIWPVNVPAWAURTVNWPWOVMVNWOWPCWABUSUTSVAVBVCVDVFWEWLGQJWCQRWBEWDW
      KWCQNVEVGVHVIVFVJFBEGVQABCDVKVL $.
      $( [2-Sep-2009] $)
  $}

  ${
    $d M m n r s u $.  $d J m n r s u $.  $d X m n r s u $.  $d F m n r s u $.
    $d Y m n r s u $.  $d A m n r s u $.
    lmtlm.1 $e |- J = ( MetOpen ` M ) $.
    lmtlm.2 $e |- X = dom dom M $.
    $( Metric space limits are topological limits under the standard topology.
       (Contributed by Jeff Madsen, 2-Sep-2009.) $)
    lmtlm $p |- ( ( M e. Met /\ Y e. A /\ F : NN --> X ) ->
                              ( F ( ~~>t ` J ) Y <-> F ( ~~>m ` M ) Y ) ) $=
      ( vm vn vr wcel cn cfv wral wa wbr wi crp wb vu vs cme wf w3a cuni cv cuz
      wrex csn cnei cc0 clt cle co ctlm clm wceq uniopn2 3ad2ant1 eleq2d anbi1d
      cr cbl blnei 3expia 3ad2antl1 imp eleq2 rexralbidv rcla4va cz eluz syl2an
      biimprd expimpd adantl imim1d simpll3 simpl ffvelrn ex simp1 sylanl1 expr
      elbl3 an32s syld adantr pm5.74d sylibd exp4a ralimdv2 reximdva syl5 mpand
      nnz ralrimdva wss neibl breq2 imbi2d rcla4v imdistani impexp elnnuz sylbi
